Lightning Components
LWC API version 61.0 provides ElementInternals Web API support and several bug fixes.

Visualforce
Check if all unmanaged Visualforce pages are served on the force.com domain.
Apex
New Apex cursors for breaking up SOQL query result processing.
Use SOQL in Apex and mock SOQL tests for Data Cloud objects.
Apex supports SOQL relationship queries that traverse up to five levels of parent-child records.

API
Update records using external IDs and interact with an improved OpenAPI spec sObjects REST API.

Packaging
Create apps to sell and distribute on AppExchange using second-generation managed packages.
Development Environments
Use Developer Edition orgs, sandboxes, and scratch orgs for developing and testing features.

Platform Development Tools
Build applications collaboratively and deliver continuously with Salesforce DX.
Heroku
Build, deliver, monitor, and scale innovative apps fast using Heroku.
Salesforce Functions
Retiring on January 31, 2025. Learn about the retirement plan.
AppExchange Partners
Search for packages by name, ID, or version number in the AppExchange Partner Console.

New and Changed Items for Developers
Find new and changed objects, calls, classes, components, commands, and more that help you customize Salesforce features.
